39:40.778 --> 39:44.013
â™ª don't...

39:44.015 --> 39:47.016
â™ª don't let me go...

39:47.018 --> 39:48.551
How is the king?

39:48.553 --> 39:49.619
Resting.

39:50.921 --> 39:52.989
I would like to stay
for a while.

39:53.958 --> 39:57.627
â™ª don't let me go

40:00.765 --> 40:07.003
â™ª run to me in the rising dawn

40:10.508 --> 40:13.510
â™ª forever we'll be holding on.

